original_title: Rui Sinel de Cordes: O Início
overview: ‘O Início É o Fim’ it's a stand-up show split in half.  'O Início' talks about all humanity's history up to 2020 as seen by the eyes of Rui Sinel de Cordes - how he thinks everything happened.  Light and Darkness.
title: Rui Sinel de Cordes: O Início
